What you need to know:  He also made a stopover at the Ndura Athletics Training Camp in Kitale, Trans Nzoia County.“I’m impressed by the private stadium at the Ndura Athletics Training Camp which also has a gym and this is good for upcoming athletes. The Youth sub-committee will also consider this facility for the holiday camps because we had a few of them who participated last year during the World Under-20 Champions among them Noah Kibet, who won bronze medal in the 800m race," he added.